---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Cake Prices, Sizes and Flavours" description="Starting cake prices, sizes and flavour options from GyulRose Cakes in Haywards Heath, West Sussex.">
  <section class="section section--blush"><div class="container"><p class="eyebrow">Plan your order</p><h1>Sizes, starting prices and flavours</h1><p class="lead">These figures help you choose a realistic starting point. Every personalised cake receives a final quote after the design, servings and decoration are confirmed.</p></div></section>
  <section class="section section--white"><div class="container pricing-grid"><div><h2>Starting size guide</h2><div class="price-table"><div><strong>6 inch</strong><span>From £35</span></div><div><strong>8 inch</strong><span>From £45</span></div><div><strong>10 inch</strong><span>From £60</span></div><div><strong>12 inch</strong><span>From £75</span></div><div><strong>14 inch</strong><span>From £90</span></div><div><strong>16 inch</strong><span>From £120</span></div></div></div><div class="quote-card"><h2>What changes the quote?</h2><ul><li>Number of servings and cake size</li><li>Number of tiers</li><li>Handmade models, toppers or sugar flowers</li><li>Detailed piping, fondant work or edible prints</li><li>Fresh flowers, macarons and specialist decorations</li><li>Delivery distance and safe setup requirements</li></ul><a class="button" href="/order/">Request your quote</a></div></div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="container"><p class="eyebrow">Flavour ideas</p><h2>Flavours shown across the gallery</h2><p class="lead">The existing portfolio includes combinations using vanilla, chocolate, strawberry, blueberry, lemon, coffee, pistachio, Oreo, Biscoff, red velvet, carrot, mascarpone, honey and Napoleon-style layers. Availability, recipe, filling and allergens must be confirmed for the specific order.</p><div class="notice"><strong>Allergy or intolerance?</strong><p>Tell GyulRose before ordering. Do not rely only on a gallery description because recipes and decorations can change.</p><a href="/allergens/">Read the allergen information</a></div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .pricing-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr; gap:50px; align-items:start; }
  .price-table { border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  .price-table div { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:20px; padding:16px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  .quote-card,.notice { background:var(--blush); border-radius:var(--radius); padding:28px; }
  .quote-card li { margin-bottom:10px; }
  .notice { max-width:780px; margin-top:30px; }
  @media(max-width:800px){.pricing-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.price-table div{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column;gap:3px}}
</style>
